parameters.name: maxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to return in this request. The default value is 100.

nested_items.name: serviceManagedS3
nested_items.description: Used to store channel data in an S3 bucket managed by IoT Analytics.

nested_items.name: customerManagedS3
nested_items.description: Used to store channel data in an S3 bucket that you manage.

nested_items.name: bucket
nested_items.description: The name of the S3 bucket in which channel data is stored.

nested_items.name: keyPrefix
nested_items.description: (Optional) The prefix used to create the keys of the channel data objects. Each object in an S3 bucket has a key that is its unique identifier within the bucket (each object in a bucket has exactly one key). The prefix must end with a forward slash (/).

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the role that grants IoT Analytics permission to interact with your Amazon S3 resources.

nested_items.name: lastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The last time the channel was updated.

nested_items.name: lastMessageArrivalTime
nested_items.description: The last time when a new message arrived in the channel.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to retrieve the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.
